{"tid":861690,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[記者再爆料] 除IU續約條件, 更有一行為令業界震驚","createTime":"2018-10-14T10:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T18:17:42.000Z","uid":34643,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"839afae2b0673169b95bf04bf555a6ae2bfe4327","tid":861690,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"IU team真的是一個溫暖有愛的團隊。IU提出的續約條件是保留IU team，並給IU team的員工加工資？據悉IU與經紀公司的合約到期，在談續約條件的時候，IU表示續約可以不另外收簽約金，取而代之的條件是保證雇佣IU team每個工作人員，以及給他們加工資。<br />\n<br />\n老板如此，員工何求？小編真想振臂高呼：這樣的好老板，麻煩給我來一打。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=1948079640,3931573718&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=572&amp;h=312&amp;s=4C02E51B134255494CF445DA000050B2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fss0.baidu.com%2F6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fit%2Fu%3D1948079640%2C3931573718%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D572%26h%3D312%26s%3D4C02E51B134255494CF445DA000050B2&h=bfe9a25a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除掉要求保留員工並加工資，IU還對IU team做過很多暖心的舉動。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">IU曾經給結婚的IU team的員工送過一輛奔馳</span></strong></span>。出手真是大方。<br />\n<br />\n不管是經紀人，還是保鏢，還是造型師，IU對IU team裡的每一個人都關懷備至，實至名歸的IU team Leader。當然，IU如此喜愛自己的工作人員，自然也是因為IU team的盡職盡責，忠心耿耿。<br />\n<br />\n這也就不奇怪，為什麼IU提出的續約條件會要求保留IU team。能在這樣溫暖的集體工作，真的是讓人實名羨慕啊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b335c5eabeef7838af184a0897660cff284def53","tid":861690,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"請問娘娘收唔收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9655ca9ec31fe8ad224dbec11eb88646e39e09c8","tid":861690,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"